==Spanish==

===Transitive verb===
'''jalar'''

# to [[pull]]
# (''familiar'') to [[draw]] (in); to [[attract]]
#: ''El circo jala todos los hijos del pueblo.'' - "The circus draws all the town's children."
#: ''Los dramatizaciones lo jalan.'' - "The plays appeal to him."

===Intransitive verb===
'''jalar'''

# to [[pull]] (together)
# (''familiar'') to [[hurry]] along; to get along
# (''Mexico, familiar'') to [[function]] properly; to be in [[working order]]

